import {
  ModuleRegistry,
  ColumnAutoSizeModule,
  ColumnHoverModule,
  RowAutoHeightModule,
  RowStyleModule,
  PaginationModule,
  CellStyleModule,
  TextFilterModule,
  NumberFilterModule,
  DateFilterModule,
  ExternalFilterModule,
  CsvExportModule,
  ColumnApiModule,
  RowApiModule,
  CellApiModule,
  RenderApiModule,
  ClientSideRowModelModule,
  CustomFilterModule,
} from 'ag-grid-community';

export const setupAGGridModules = () => {
  ModuleRegistry.registerModules([
    ColumnAutoSizeModule,
    ColumnHoverModule,
    RowAutoHeightModule,
    RowStyleModule,
    PaginationModule,
    CellStyleModule,
    TextFilterModule,
    NumberFilterModule,
    DateFilterModule,
    ExternalFilterModule,
    CsvExportModule,
    ColumnApiModule,
    RowApiModule,
    CellApiModule,
    RenderApiModule,
    ClientSideRowModelModule,
    CustomFilterModule,
  ]);
};
